articles.title: ‘Daredevil’ Hits Reset Button as Marvel Overhauls Its TV Business - Hollywood Reporter
articles.description: Launched during the pandemic with a playbook to shoot $150 million-plus seasons with no pilots, the Disney unit is undergoing growing pains and seeing the logic of "traditional TV culture."
